OL,3,CMeasures to be brought forward to
OL,4,C'begin process of repealing Legacy Act'
OL,6,FMeasures are to be brought forward to
OL,7,F"begin the process" of repealing the
OL,8,Fprevious government's controversial
OL,9,FLegacy Act.
OL,11,FThe King confirmed the move in his
OL,12,Fspeech at the State Opening of
OL,13,FParliament on Wednesday.
OL,15,FLabour's plan is to bring forward
OL,16,Fmeasures to begin the process of
OL,17,Frepealing and replacing the Act that
OL,18,Fgained royal assent just last year.
