OL,3,CMeasures to be brought forward to
OL,4,C'begin process of repealing Legacy Act'
OL,6,FWhile the entire Act cannot be
OL,7,Frepealed without something in place to
OL,8,Freplace it, the government is expected
OL,9,Fto repeal the controversial policy of
OL,10,Foffering conditional immunity for
OL,11,FTroubles crimes.
OL,13,FThe Act, aimed at addressing the
OL,14,Flegacy of Northern Ireland's past, has
OL,15,Fbeen almost universally opposed by
OL,16,Fparties and victims' groups.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
