OL,3,CMeasures to be brought forward to
OL,4,C'begin process of repealing Legacy Act'
OL,6,FEarlier this year, then shadow
OL,7,FSecretary of State for Northern
OL,8,FIreland Hilary Benn indicated they
OL,9,Fwould not scrap the ICRIR, which is
OL,10,Fled by retired judge Sir Declan
OL,11,FMorgan, but wanted to see if it could
OL,12,Fcommand the confidence of victims'
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FThere have been legal challenges to
OL,16,Fthe Act, including an interstate case
OL,17,Fby the Irish government under the
OL,18,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
