OL,3,CMeasures to be brought forward to
OL,4,C'begin process of repealing Legacy Act'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a legal challenge by
OL,7,FTroubles victims to the Act saw a
OL,8,Flengthy judgment issued in February.
OL,9,FIt found that conditional immunity
OL,10,Ffrom prosecutions for Troubles crimes
OL,11,Fis in breach of the European
OL,12,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,14,FHowever, the same judgment also found
OL,15,Fthat the ICRIR to be independent and
OL,16,Fcapable of conducting human rights-
OL,17,Fcompliant investigations.
